data.title: Vaults of Terra - (Space Marine) Chapters - Deathwatch
data.description:
The Vaults of Terra presents the lore of the Deathwatch, the alliance of Space Marine chapters that forms the Inquisition's elite Xenos fighting units.

As always, vote below for what chapter you would like to feature next on the Vaults of Terra.

data.title: Vaults of Terra - (Space Marine) Chapters - Iron Hands
data.description:
The Vaults of Terra introduce the final video before the start of the Imperial guard Series, the Iron Hands Space Marine chapter, whose will is as hard as the metal for which they're named.

The Imperial Guard will be starting next video, so vote for what you want to see when we start talking about the Hammer of the Emperor, along with your votes for chapters in the on-going chapter's series.
